The Great Jahy, the Dark Realm’s second-in-command, cuts a frightening figure, feared and revered by all. But when a run-in with a magical girl results in the destruction of the precious mana crystal, the Dark Realm falls, transporting the newly puny and powerless Jahy to the human world! Unfortunately, plotting the revival of the Dark Realm from a cramped, crumbling one-room apartment is no easy feat when you have rent to pay and a job to keep!
(Source: Square Enix Manga & Books)

Takane Takamine’s stripping isn’t merely to tease—it’s the key to unleashing her time-bending powers! Follow the adventures of this powerful beauty and her walking "closet"—the friendless nobody Koushi Shirota!
(Source: Yen Press) <i>Note: Nominated for the Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Manga Category.<i>

Ooyama-kun normally doesn’t get involved with Akutsu-san, a delinquent girl in his class, but for some reason she makes his house her hang-out place! Will Ooyama do something horrible to her behind closed doors or will he chase her out? But dealing with Akutsu-san’s sexy, cute behavior in such a confined space… he’s sure to get flustered! He wants her to go home, but he doesn’t? A teasing comedy under a single roof!
